8. Contributing
---------------

Patches are welcome.  Please ensure:

  - cargo clippy --workspace --all-targets -- -D warnings passes clean
  - cargo test --workspace passes
  - No unwrap()/expect() in library crates
  - Public APIs carry /// doc comments
  - Satellite-specific logic belongs in TOML, not in Rust
  - Commits are signed (git commit -s) with ASCII-only messages
